Allowed values are \f[V]info\f[R], \f[V]warn\f[R], and \f[V]error\f[R].
The default value is \f[V]warn\f[R]
.RE
.SS Analyzers
.PP
\f[V]dotnet format analyzers\f[R] - Formats code to match \f[V]editorconfig\f[R] settings for analyzers.
.SH DESCRIPTION
.PP
